headline: GoDaddy's New ANS Marketplace Tells You Which AI Agents You Can Trust
summary: GoDaddy (NYSE: GDDY) today announced the next phase of its Agent Name Service (ANS), unveiling the new ANS Marketplace at www.GoDaddy.com/ANS – along with a set of new AI agents people can try today. The ANS Marketplace gives entrepreneurs, developers and platforms a way to discover ANS-verified agents, understand how they work and see ANS trust signals in action.

headline: Is GoDaddy Stock Underperforming the S&P 500?
summary: GoDaddy has substantially underperformed the S&P 500 over the past year, yet analysts remain moderately bullish on the stock’s prospects.
